snippet.title: BLINK The Last Night Trailer
snippet.description:
A vengeful entity comes to kidnap the girl you're babysitting. Guide your way through various psychological twists and turns as you begin to realize that not everything is as it seems. BLINK: The Last Night is the first chapter of a psychological horror story.

Trailer music provided by PhatPhoneBook, check out more of his work: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/PhatPhoneBook/videos
